{
  "3210820": {
    "name": "DRONE PERSPECTIVE Demo",
    "steam_appid": 3210820,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210820/extras/20b928d166ad729dff4628ee7aff9f38.avif?t=1742986336\" width=616 height=250 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I am happy to present you a demo for my upcoming game - Drone Perspective.<br> <br>This demo includes: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 Story missions connected into the first act of a conspiracy story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level Editor - unlocks during the story, allows you to create your own combat simulations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Community Workshop support to share your simulation with others and play community created content</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In-Game files and emails focused on world-building.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gameplay is the same as in the full version.<br>  I broadcast latest available gameplay on the main product page.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join me on Live Stream for Steam Next Fest: Monday 14 October. 19:00 CEST.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Real-time tactics focused on simulating modern firefights guided from the drone.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take the lead of five brave soldiers, split into three squads: Alpha, Bravo, and Charlie.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Orchestrate actions of your troops in real-time from the drone flying above the battlefield.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Suppress your enemies and storm their positions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use variety of equipment such as rocket launchers, bomb-drones, or artillery barrage to crack especially tough defense.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid casualties.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210820/extras/10c5fd4d1f91ec7e13d708b464f12130.poster.avif?t=1742986336\" width=650 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210820/extras/10c5fd4d1f91ec7e13d708b464f12130.webm?t=1742986336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210820/extras/10c5fd4d1f91ec7e13d708b464f12130.mp4?t=1742986336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your country is invaded. Military organization VEIL invites you to join as a tester for their new drone-based warfare communication system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can impact the situation on the battlefield directly from your home PC. Connect to the variety of drones and provide guidance to the troops in the field.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some of our troops are equipped with the new generation of combat visors and will be able to receive your direct guidance from the sky.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They put trust in you and will shoot or move wherever you tell them, but be careful and weigh every step, because the price of your mistake is someone’s life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Meta-Gameplay</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use in-game operation system called VEIL OS to connect to your missions. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage emails, install and maintain OS software to make sure you're using up-to-date technology. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Witness eerie events and try to uncover the truth in the conspiracy surrounding your employer,  VEIL CORP. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use help from the outside to affect the fabric of in-game reality and change the outcome of existing events. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be careful whom you trust. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Equipment</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If the situation is dire, use bomb drone to clean your way. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210820/extras/6b28ded2c3937e329933582f05c4f807.poster.avif?t=1742986336\" width=778 height=434 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210820/extras/6b28ded2c3937e329933582f05c4f807.webm?t=1742986336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210820/extras/6b28ded2c3937e329933582f05c4f807.mp4?t=1742986336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or rocket launchers, to find the new ways of resolving tactical puzzles. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210820/extras/712ce9fefe1dcaa3216d8ef4abb9f7e4.poster.avif?t=1742986336\" width=626 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210820/extras/712ce9fefe1dcaa3216d8ef4abb9f7e4.webm?t=1742986336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210820/extras/712ce9fefe1dcaa3216d8ef4abb9f7e4.mp4?t=1742986336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use desktop environment called VEIL OS to connect to your missions and to navigate through conspiracies in reality-bending meta-gameplay.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210820/extras/a366400e5c88d94201466d33a26f61e5.avif?t=1742986336\" width=680 height=382 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own combat experiences and share them with other drone operators in Community Workshop.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210820/extras/abde42b474ada6d0bf48c1b13bf12515.poster.avif?t=1742986336\" width=800 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210820/extras/abde42b474ada6d0bf48c1b13bf12515.webm?t=1742986336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210820/extras/abde42b474ada6d0bf48c1b13bf12515.mp4?t=1742986336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is an independent solo project.<br>if you're interested and want to see latest updates or want to share anything related to the game, I will be happy to see you in project Discord, Instagram or TikTok.</p>",
